               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 4ra-101vb)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 4ra-6vb)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 6vb-8va)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 8va-9rb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 110 miracles (fols. 9ra-101vb)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi ... "Does not the man ...": 33 strophes (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 10rb-35va)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus": 1 miracle (fols. 101vb-102ra)&#xD;
III) Taʾāmra Takla Hāymānot "Miracles of Takla Haymanot": 1 miracle (fol. 102ra-rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-3.</summary>
